The paper proposes a transfer deep learning framework for multimodal data, specifically for audio-visual recognition. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as embeddings, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves multimodal data, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The sub-category cs.SD (Sound) is also a possibility, but it is less likely given that the paper focuses on both audio and visual modalities.
